    Filter is_regexp_match["a.*", case_insensitive=true](#0{s})
      Map (replace(#0{s}, "\n", "<newline>"))
        ReadStorage materialize.public.t

Source materialize.public.t
  filter=(is_regexp_match["a.*", case_insensitive=true](#0{s}))

Target cluster: multiprocess

EOF

query T
